com.teamdev.jxbrowser.chromium.swing

Class DefaultPopupHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.teamdev.jxbrowser.chromium.swing.DefaultPopupHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PopupHandler 

    public class DefaultPopupHandler
extends java.lang.Object
implements PopupHandler
    Represents default implementation of the PopupHandler that will display popup Browser in a JFrame. The frame will be positioned according to the initial popup bounds. If popup doesn't provide initial bounds the frame will have 800x600 size and its location will be decided by OS.
    表示PopupHandler的默认实现，它将在JFrame中显示弹出浏览器。框架将根据初始弹出边界定位。如果弹出窗口不提供初始边界，则框架的尺寸将为800x600，其位置将由操作系统决定。
